mappings.name: List the apps under the specified AdMob account.

schema.description: Response for the apps list request.

apps.description: The resulting apps for the requested account.

nextPageToken.description: If not empty, indicates that there may be more apps for the request; this value should be passed in a new `ListAppsRequest`.

mappings.name: List the ad units under the specified AdMob account.

schema.description: Response for the ad units list request.

adUnits.description: The resulting ad units for the requested account.

nextPageToken.description: If not empty, indicates that there may be more ad units for the request; this value should be passed in a new `ListAdUnitsRequest`.
Used to set the `page_token` in the `ListAdSourcesRequest` to retrieve the next page. If this field is omitted, there are no subsequent pages.

mappings.name: Gets information about the specified AdMob publisher account.

schema.description: A publisher account contains information relevant to the use of this API, such as the time zone used for the reports.

currencyCode.description: Currency code of the earning-related metrics, which is the 3-letter code defined in ISO 4217. The daily average rate is used for the currency conversion.

name.description: Resource name of this account. Format is accounts/{publisher_id}.

publisherId.description: The unique ID by which this publisher account can be identified in the API requests (for example, pub-1234567890).

reportingTimeZone.description: The time zone that is used in reports that are generated for this account. The value is a time-zone ID as specified by the CLDR project, for example, "America/Los_Angeles".

schema.description: Response for the publisher account list request.

account.description: Publisher that the client credentials can access.

nextPageToken.description: If not empty, indicates that there might be more accounts for the request; you must pass this value in a new `ListPublisherAccountsRequest`.
